# License Agreement

## 1. Definitions

- **"Software"** refers to the code, documentation, and other materials included in this repository.
- **"Individual Use"** refers to the use of the Software by a single person for personal, educational, or non-commercial purposes.
- **"Small Business"** refers to an entity with fewer than 10 employees.
- **"Medium Business"** refers to an entity with 10 to 50 employees.
- **"Enterprise Business"** refers to an entity with more than 50 employees.
- **"Government Use"** refers to the use of the Software by any governmental agency or institution.

