- **Small Businesses**: Small businesses are granted the same rights as individuals for both non-commercial and commercial purposes, provided they do not have 10 or more employees.

### 2.2. Paid Use for Medium Businesses

- **Medium Businesses**: For commercial use by medium businesses (entities with 10 to 50 employees), a paid license is required. This license can be obtained by becoming a sponsor on [GitHub Sponsors](https://github.com/sponsors/noscrape) with a contribution of at least €5 per month.

### 2.3. Paid Use for Enterprise Businesses and Government Use

- **Enterprise Businesses and Government Use**: For commercial use by enterprise businesses (entities with more than 50 employees) and any governmental agencies or institutions, a paid license is required. This license can be obtained by becoming a sponsor on [GitHub Sponsors](https://github.com/sponsors/noscrape) with a contribution of at least €50 per month.

